---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/main.astro";

const lastUpdated = "April 19, 2025";
---

<MainLayout
  title="Terms & Conditions - Smiling Dev Consulting"
  description="Terms and conditions for using Smiling Dev Consulting services."
>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Terms & Conditions</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-8">Last Updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2>1. Services</h2>
          <p>
            Smiling Dev Consulting ("we," "us," or "our") provides web development, technical consulting, 
            and digital transformation services to clients. By engaging our services, you agree to these terms and conditions.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2>2. Project Terms</h2>
          <p>
            All projects begin with a written agreement outlining scope, deliverables, timeline, and payment terms. 
            Changes to project scope must be agreed upon in writing.
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Project timelines are estimates and subject to change based on project complexity and client feedback</li>
            <li>Final deliverables are provided upon receipt of full payment</li>
            <li>Source code ownership transfers to the client upon final payment</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2>3. Payment Terms</h2>
          <p>
            Our standard payment terms include:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>50% deposit required to begin work</li>
            <li>Remaining balance due upon project completion</li>
            <li>Additional work beyond agreed scope billed at our standard hourly rate</li>
            <li>Late payments subject to 1.5% monthly interest charge</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2>4. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p>
            Upon final payment, clients receive full rights to the completed project deliverables. 
            We retain rights to:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Display the work in our portfolio</li>
            <li>Describe the project in case studies</li>
            <li>Use non-proprietary code components in other projects</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2>5. Confidentiality</h2>
          <p>
            We maintain strict confidentiality regarding client information and project details. 
            Non-disclosure agreements available upon request.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2>6. Warranty & Support</h2>
          <p>
            We provide:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>30-day bug fix warranty on all delivered work</li>
            <li>Documentation for all completed projects</li>
            <li>Optional ongoing support and maintenance packages</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2>7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>
            Our liability is limited to the amount paid for services. We are not liable for indirect, 
            consequential, or incidental damages.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2>8. Termination</h2>
          <p>
            Either party may terminate services with 30 days written notice. Client is responsible for 
            payment for all work completed up to termination date.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2>9. Governing Law</h2>
          <p>
            These terms are governed by the laws of the State of Utah, United States. 
            Any disputes will be resolved in Salt Lake City, Utah.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>10. Contact</h2>
          <p>
            Questions about these terms should be sent to:{' '}
            <a href="mailto:info@smiling.dev" class="text-primary hover:text-primary/80">
              info@smiling.dev
            </a>
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>